force him down.

Quickstrike:

Quickstrike ducked, suddenly seeing Bobertron jump out and fire. He lost his
grip on Cheetor, sending him stumbling to the ground. He lunged up and
grabbed for Bobertron. "Hey! That cat belongs t' th' Preds now!" He dug his
fangs in his leg.
